org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface Connection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Documentable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AlarmsEventsConnection, DataAccessConnection
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlarmsEventsConnectionImpl, ConnectionImpl, DataAccessConnectionImpl

    public interface Connection
extends Documentable
    A representation of the model object 'Connection'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Endpoint
    • Endpoint Label
    • Credentials
    • Timeout

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getConnection()
